
Privacy Policy

KrishiSat

Effective Date: November 10, 2024

Welcome to KrishiSat, a weather forecasting application that provides real-time weather data based on users' current location. This privacy policy explains how XBOSON AI PVT LTD ("we," "our," or "us") collects, uses, and protects your information while using KrishiSat. By accessing or using our application, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information to provide you with weather data and improve our services:

Location Data: To provide accurate weather information based on your location, we collect location data from your device when the app is in use.
Device Information: We may collect information about your device, including the type, operating system, and unique identifiers, to maintain and enhance the application’s functionality.
Usage Data: We may gather anonymized information about how you use the app to help us improve our services.
2. How We Use Your Information

The information collected is primarily used for:

Providing Weather Data: Your location data enables us to deliver real-time, accurate weather updates for your current location.
Improving Application Performance: Usage and device data help us diagnose issues, enhance app performance, and optimize user experience.
We do not use your personal information for advertising or promotional purposes without your consent.

3. Sharing Your Information

We prioritize the confidentiality of your information and do not share your data with third parties, except:

With Service Providers: We may share information with trusted third-party service providers to enhance app performance or process data on our behalf. These providers are bound by confidentiality agreements.
For Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information when required by law or to protect our rights, safety, and the security of others.
4. Data Security

We use industry-standard measures to safeguard your data. While we strive to protect your information, no transmission over the internet or mobile networks is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.

5. Data Retention

We retain your information only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, comply with legal obligations, or resolve disputes.

6. Your Choices and Rights

You have the right to:

Opt-Out of Location Services: You may disable location tracking through your device’s settings, but this may limit app functionality.
Request Data Access or Deletion: You may contact us to request access to or deletion of your personal data, subject to legal restrictions.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We encourage you to review this policy periodically. Your continued use of KrishiSat after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated terms.

8. Contact Us

For questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at:

